name: HOOVABIKE NOVA01
description:
Originally designed for high-speed racing, converting the form of angler fish head with the core material used phenomenal umbral steel. Personal modification and owned by Alpha Geli. Commonly used for hunting & gathering.

NOVA01 was 3.4 meters long by 2.5 meters wide. It's power system was an AmeGem Xr.1 with fusion bio-mecha turbine. It had twin Iure rod on the tail.

Manufactured in year 5, Geli Exo Planet.
